-- Ecuador Credit Card Rules Challenge Banks, Fitch Ratings Says
-- B y   N a t h a n   G i l l
-- 2012-06-29T17:07:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/ecuador-credit-card-rules-challenge-banks-fitch-ratings-says.html
Ecuador’s rules prohibiting banks
from charging customers for some credit card services may reduce
revenue,  Fitch Ratings  said.  “Ecuadorian banks will be challenged to diversify income
and maintain improvements in profitability achieved in 2011 over
the long term,” the ratings company said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
